<DocsLayout title="Documentation" description="Learn how Bloktastic works, how to install components, and how to contribute.">
  <h1>Documentation</h1>

  <p>
    Bloktastic is an open registry for Storyblok components and plugins. It combines reusable schemas with
    high-quality prompts so teams can generate framework-specific frontend code quickly.
  </p>

  <h2>What You Get</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Installable Bloks</strong> with manifest metadata and Storyblok schema files.</li>
    <li><strong>Prompt-First Workflow</strong> for AI-assisted code generation in your stack.</li>
    <li><strong>CLI Tools</strong> to search, install, and validate packages.</li>
    <li><strong>Curated Plugins</strong> for editor field and workflow enhancements.</li>
  </ul>

