  <h2>Prompt-First Model</h2>

  <ol>
    <li><strong>Schema</strong>: pushed to Storyblok as component definition.</li>
    <li><strong>Prompt</strong>: guides AI toward a production-ready implementation with accessibility and edge cases.</li>
  </ol>

  <p>
    This avoids shipping dozens of framework templates. Instead, each team generates code that matches its own
    architecture conventions.
  </p>
